<sect1 id="quality_assurance">
	<title>Copyright Statements</title>
	<sect2>
		<title>Current Year Definition</title>
		<para>In copyright statements, the current year is defined. Each year, it must be updated at the following places (files):
		</para>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				<para>Header in Java source files
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>feature.xml files
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>About dialog (de.rcenvironment.core.start/about.mappings)
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>Splash images ([..].gui.branding.[..]/splash.bmp)
				</para>
			</listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
	</sect2>
</sect1>